DESCRIPTION:Join us on Wednesday\, April 8th from 4–7 PM at Whispering Vine South Creek for a tasting featuring the polished\, expressive wines of HALL Winery\, one of Napa Valley’s most celebrated producers. This lineup highlights Hall’s signature style across Cabernet Sauvignon\, Merlot\, and Sauvignon Blanc.\nTasting Fee: $30 (Buy a bottle from the tasting and your fee is refunded)\nFeatured Wines:\n• Hall Cabernet Sauvignon 2022 – Dark berry fruit\, black cherry\, graphite\, and ripe plum unfold over a full\, supple palate with polished oak and a long\, energetic finish.\n• Hall Napa Valley Merlot 2019 – Deep and luxurious with violet\, ripe cherry\, baking spice\, cocoa\, and dusty tannins framed by lingering graphite notes.\n• Hall Napa Valley Sauvignon Blanc 2024 – Bright and vibrant with tropical fruit\, citrus\, lilikoi\, lemon curd\, white flowers\, and a crisp mineral finish.\nExplore the elegance and balance that define Hall’s Napa Valley wines—buy a bottle and your tasting is free.
LOCATION:85 Foothill Rd Ste 1 Reno\, NV 89511
SUMMARY:HALL Winery Tasting
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR